title: WATCH: Top Royal Rumble moves
text:
WWE Royal Rumble: Watch the top moves from Sunday night's show Kevin Owens, AJ Styles, Bayley and more make the cut   6:44am We've picked out the best moves from the Royal Rumble 2017, including ones from Kevin Owens and AJ Styles. Kevin Owens thundering Roman Reigns through a table and AJ Styles clocking John Cena with a Phenomenal Forearm make the cut in our video of best moves from the Royal Rumble. Book the show on Sky Sports Box Office 
Owens splashed Reigns through the pine during the pair's Universal Title tussle, while Styles cracked Cena as he aimed to keep his WWE Title - and stop his opponent winning a record-equalling 16th. 
Bayley, Rich Swann and Jack Gallagher also feature, while Owens figures again with his Stunner, a move that got the master of the manoeuvre, Stone Cold Steve Austin, talking on Twitter! Damn. I guess I gotta teach @FightOwensFight how to do a GD Stone Cold Stunner. Put some stink on it, kid. @WWE #royalrumble — Steve Austin (@steveaustinBSR) January 30, 2017 
Check out those efforts, and a whole lot more, in the video above - then watch a full repeat of WWE Royal Rumble between 10am on Monday and 8pm on Thursday on Sky Sports Box Office. 
WWE Royal Rumble booking details 
WWE Royal Rumble will repeated on Sky Sports Box Office (channel 491) BUT NOT Sky Sports HD Box Office (channel 492) between 10am on Monday, January 30 and 8pm on Thursday, February 2 - 8pm is the start of the final playout. 
The pay-per-view will cost £19.95 for viewers in the United Kingdom and €24.95 for customers in the Republic of Ireland. 
You can order the show by visiting this link: https://my.sky.com/orderboxoffice/?DCMP=WWERoyalRumble 
You can also book the event over the phone: UK viewers should call 03442 410 888, while customers in the Republic of Ireland should call 0818 220 225. (There may be an additional charge for telephone bookings). 
You can also order the show via your Sky remote: 
Sky+: Press the box office button on your remote, then click the sports tab followed by WWE Royal Rumble. 
Sky Q: Press Home on your Sky Q remote, select TV guide, then Box Office and then WWE Royal Rumble. Enter your TV Pin if prompted. (Only bookings via Sky TV remote are recordable using Sky Plus).
